title: Johnny Depp (People in the news)(pdf){Zzzzz}
description:
In his rise to fame, Johnny Depp overcame an unstable childhood, drug abuse, and a series of public scandals. Today, with his troubled past behind him, Depp's talent for playing eccentric characters has made him one of the most respected actors in Hollywood.

Publisher: Lucent (April 30, 2004)
Language: English
ISBN-10: 1590185382
ISBN-13: 978-1590185384

A Look in Johnny Depp's Life
A Kid's Review on March 24, 2005
I highly recommend this book for people who like Johnny Depp and what he's done. This book pointed out that like a lot of hollywood stars some of them came from a hard childhood, to a hard teenlife and has turned into a well respected adult. This includes Johnny Depp. Most people wouldn't have figured out that he once owned a club, used to drugs, and even had a beautiful daughter. If you love some of the movies that Johnny Depp has stared in then you will find a new respect for Johnny Depp in this biography.
